    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.44 - ((tmp + 0.50 / v0 + 0.38) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.68)))
    v1 = (wp.abs(v0) * (wp.abs(v2 + 0.10) + (v2 + 0.90 * v0 + 0.54)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v0 + 0.02 - v0 + 0.26)))
    tmp = (0.00 * wp.sin((v1 + 0.84 - tmp + 0.22)))
    tmp = (0.96 * v1)
